For the king is that when he spawns he is one of two lvls, the higher one will argo a 60 and a 61, so he would also add to a 57, the lower one wont argo a 61 (I am sure) and might agro a 60 (not sure), so a 57 I would doubt be able to pull him. If you want to check, have abscond up, snare a warrior and if he starts to run to you, run UP the cliff to the top and abscond, you should be able to get it off before he gets to you.<br>
